longBusinessSummary: Celltrion Pharm, Inc., a pharmaceutical company, develops and sells biosimilars and over-the-counter drugs in South Korea. The company offers hepatotonic, anti-inflammatory, antihistamine, respiratory apparatus, circulary system, digestive and stomachic, hormone/metabolic disease, antibiotic/antimycotic, nutrientia and tonic, immunology, oncology, and other drugs. It serves university hospitals and general pharmacies. Celltrion Pharm Inc. was founded in 1976 and is based in Cheongju, South Korea.
